Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shimogamo Shrine is located
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the triangular area surrounded by the Takano and Kamo rivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:10.32,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(938,324,1307,172,0,2152)}Lake Biwa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although there are mountains of shrines with noble lineages in Kyoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:13.24,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(503,220,-88,147,0,2862)}Kamo River
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:13.45,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(843,550,1203,645,0,3070)}Takano River
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimogamo Shrine is one of the foremost
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:15.45,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,393)\move(988,277,1002,218,0,2240)}Shimogamo Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,among the ones that existed prior to the Heian period.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though scores of visitors go there throughout the year
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:18.99,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,267)}God\Nof matchmaking\NAioi\NShrine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to receive matchmaking and all kinds of other blessings from the gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,few know that a small ramen cart appears in the vicinity each and every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Cat Ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rumor is it uses actual cats to make the broth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but whether that's true or not cannot be ascertained.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the taste is unmatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a person of Shimogamo Yuusuisou, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact I am a resident of Shimogamo Yuusuisou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:00:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimogamo Yuusuisou is a boarding house behind Eizan Demachiyanagi Station,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's apparently exactly the same as it was since it was rebuilt after it disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during the violence of the final days of the Tokugawa shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for the light leaking out the windows, it would be no different than ruins,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when I visited there at the introduction of the University Co-op at the start of school,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's no wonder I thought I'd accidentally stumbled into Kowloon city.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered that I have spotted this queer, curious fellow quite a number of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a god of Shimogamo Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My proper name is Kamotaketsunuminokami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.30,0:01:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kamotake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamotaketsunominokamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me say it twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the second time was different...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your parent's names, how you were always throwing up and making sour smells as a baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your nickname during elementary school, the middle school cultural festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your fleeting first love during high school, the first time you watched an adult video,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your life as a ronin, and your lazy, idle days spent after entering college.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After suffering romantic disappointment in the club of your dreams, unable to open up to people,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before long you started getting in the way of people's path to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why have you spent these two years in such a timid state?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:01:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because Ozu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept that you have had your soul somewhat dirtied by the influence of Ozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is not all, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The past two years go rambling through my brain like swaying paper lanterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the sacred woods of Shimogamo Shrine, of all places,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my delicate heart was seized by painful memories, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:12.32,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(636,457)}Ahhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what I wanted to scream out, but I restrained myself like a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-None of your business.  It's got nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will soon be Kannazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must travel to Izumo once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is our job, yes, but it is quite a lot of work, and don't make light of the train fare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this age we just toss everyone's proposals
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into the wooden box for "already inspected" with hardly a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet as I am a serious fellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but to be deep in thought, scratching my head
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thinking about which two people would be most suited for each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,almost like a matrimonial agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woe is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't follow in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When fall comes we gather at Izumo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and decide the relationships of man and woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the name Akashi-san, whom you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here are you and the name Ozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're even stupider than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a god of matchmaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am preparing to match this woman you know, Akashi-san, with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's between you and Ozu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you desire, come to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimogamo Yuusuisou, room 210.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This strange fellow is saying he is trying to tie akashi-san to either Ozu or me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in high school I didn't participate in any club activities
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and just stayed cooped up with a bunch of other layabout guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.15,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(998,589,1372,593,0,1272)}Singing\Nfor\N everyone!\N\N\N\N\NLet's Sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.90,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(686,255,1300,259,0,2023)}Dance Dance\NDance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.90,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(286,336,908,330,0,2023)}Judo\NClub
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.90,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(85,269,709,264,0,2023)}Cosplay
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.90,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(-50,384,424,382,0,1523)}Will\Nyou\Ntake\Nup\NSumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I was a brand-spanking new freshman university student
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and countless doors to the mystical treasure that is known as
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that "rose-coloured campus life" lay open before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was half-swooned with glee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one I chose was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.12,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,890)}Cupid
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the raven-haired maidens working up an invigorating sweat,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would begin the rally of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what I, a fool beyond all help, had thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My still-as-of-yet-rose-coloured self was cut to the quick by that which is called reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making 100 friends wouldn't be so bad, or so I frivolously thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was soon made aware of just how difficult casually getting to know other people could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish of a rally unfulfilled, I was not even able to hit back,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my serves were left unreturned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried training myself to be sociable and easy-going,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I wasn't part of the conversation to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time I realized I had to be sociable in order to be included in the conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had lost my place among the circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was then that an ominous man stood beside me with a face of ill portent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some messenger from hell that only delicate little me can see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say some pretty mean things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry, I am your compatriot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my first contact with Ozu, as well as worst contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's quite a contrast, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should mix it up over there myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.35,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(861,582,843,8,606,1648)}Shimogamo Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where the Kamo and Takano rivers join
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,below the Shimogamo Shrine is reffered to as the "Kamo river Delta",
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.69,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(827,739,933,290,0,800)}Use, concealed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.69,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(173,694)}Party Area
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is widely used as a party location for celebrating the beginning of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu is in the same year I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8 in 10 people who saw him in the dark would mistake him for a demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:38.21,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shit load of signs: http://i39.tinypic.com/2uiuofk.jpg
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the remaining two could be convinced of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating the unhappiness of others as a topping on his rice,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's a man with seriously not a single point of praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul would have surely stayed unblemished were it not for having met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you gonna turn on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just joking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop touching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the night breeze is so chilly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lonely bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... why does it have to be you next to me instead of a raven-haired maiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look.  Akashi-san came, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in the engineering department, so maybe she's designing for Birdman or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, maybe we should call it of for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get Akashi-san mixed up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?  What happened to your pride as a "Black Cupid"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure I have my pride, but to someone from the outside, this just looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're going to let your conviction bend because you're worried about what other people think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I, who have dedicated both my body and soul, am not a person such as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not here today precisely because you bear this loneliness and isolation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the ones that have lost sight of reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must bring the hammer down upon those who have lost themselves among frivolous dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, without further ado!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear ye, hear ye! For we are the ones who hinder love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now rain the heavens down upon you merrymaking ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Id... iot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we may be idiots, but you guys should watch out for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bottle rocket fireworks are for the purpose of rocketing up into the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:07.50,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(769,318)}Bottle rockets, roman candles and firecrackers are not allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing things like holding them in your hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aiming them at people, or using them to bomb people over rivers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having a peaceful, harmonious party are quite are not at all allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your ground!  Counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn barbarians!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one shallow river!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna smack you good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ozu, they're not all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I had met Ozu it was just cutting, cutting, and more cutting
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the red threads that stretched across the circle like at Yasui-konpiragu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.28,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(672,330)}Fatty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At these activities Ozu was ingenious,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there were even villainous rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that there was no personal information we did not know and make use of,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that we would scatter oil and then light fires,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.62,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(652,342)}Baldy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and whether that was true or not it was spread around
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it was an environment where we were set up as guys
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who constantly enjoyed blazing scenes of carnage here and there inside the circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like some incarnation of evil, a disgrace among all homo sapiens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after we were kicked out of the circle,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we did not let our activities slacken, we expanded globally,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and cloaked as gods of death the evil name of the "Black Cupids" roared throughout the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was a maiden in love in the east we'd say "Give up on that freak",
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or for a man in the west worried about on-sided love we'd advise
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Just give up, it's not use."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the spark of love was sprinkled in the south, we'd immediately pour water on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's said love in the north is impossible to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes our victims came close to drowning us in the canals of Lake Biwa,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surrounded the boarding house, made us hide in a manga cafe in Kitashirakawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or cried at me in the middle of Konoe Street when I spoke too frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't lose, I couldn't lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though I was sure that losing would have let me and everyone else be happier!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except for Ozu.  I could care less if he's happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I was walking, catching my breath after hacing run all the way to Kiyamachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under the overhang of someone's house
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was caught by an old woman who emitted a suspiciously ghoulish aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unplaceable aura was persuasive, and thinking logically,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was no way that the fortune-telling of a creature
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who emits such an aura could be anything but spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is a face of extreme impatience... You are unsatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel that you are not blessed with a situation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where you can make the most of your talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense your fiercely earnest talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly did I tip my hat to the old woman's keen insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To perceive my good sense and talents in an instant and yet be so very unassuming,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like how a master always hides their true ability, it made even me forget where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I sense there is an opportunity you can't let pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As in an excellent chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know what it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This opportunity is always dangling in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must grab this opportunity and act on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still somewhat vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you be more specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will walk this life as now, ever unchanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 1000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you haven't answered anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing the lost lamb?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of yours, Ozu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shameless bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell are you popular all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's just uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Force feeding me such a bundle of fungi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with these ribbed bits?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the dental hygienist at the dentist I go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:11:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looked totally drunk and asked me out for drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you've never had a young lady like that stick her fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in your mouth your entire life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bring me down to your level.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you visited the god of matchmaking at the Shimogamo Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to do it once for fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, what do you think of Akashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's between you and Ozu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had thought I was the only person unfortunate enough
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to actually be able to comprehend a human being as dumb as yourself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shush, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she might go out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd much rather have a beautiful raven-haired maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that makes you go "whoa..." than someone who is able to comprehend a person such as myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why so selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're still hung up on being dumped by Kohinata-san
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we were freshmen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say not that name in my presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll become happy in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now see here.  Akashi-san is not interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that depressed look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:11:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray for your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you I've wasted my perfectly lovely college life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  I think you're also to blame for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it doesn't matter which path you took,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd keep ending up right where you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, once I met you I put all my efforts into making you no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you haunt me so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the way I show my love!  We're connected by the black thread of fate, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.80,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(302,453)}The Japan Trench
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A chill went down my spine as a fearsome phantom rose into my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, if you want to eat any more, please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-san, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are pretty dense, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the usual place for the after-party, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Birdman Circle is camped out over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't eaten meat in a while, so if you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat after a party?  Do they have no pride as an agricultural people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ozu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He already ran out the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You escape too, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard's left me behind again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will handle the bill, so out the back.  That's what I came to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in your debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about the debt, just keep your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.  Hurry and leave, I have to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met Akashi-san the previous year during a part time job at the Shimogamo used book fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A year younger than I, said to be in the engineering department,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and meticulously prepared at anything and everything she does,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it felt like just one stare from her eyes and even a shoplifter would stay their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you do on vacations, Akashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to tell you something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that she was not someone who was asked her weekend plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent her off with a fiery cheer of "You just keep doing things your own way!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?  Don't just barge into my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you just stroll on in...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Castella.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it, so chill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You giving someone something?  That's rare...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get any lonelier than eating a giant Castella all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pining for a taste of a person's love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!  I'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably came to visit the person in this boarding house known as "the master".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Castella is surely the leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, just as Ozu said, a Castella like this is to be eaten together with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most definitely not Ozu.  Perhaps with Akashi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I was surprised that Akashi-san's name came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that strange man who called himself a god and said he was heading out to Izumo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to decide the relationships between man and woman seriously be telling the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kannazuki.  In other words, the 10th lunar month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The myriad gods gather at Izumo, leaving vacant the various lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:49.49,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(314,0)\pos(918,400)}Izumo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite well known.  Even I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And among those gods, there are sure to be some of suitable peculiarity.  That is not the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:15:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The question I have often pondered is for what reason all those gods would gather at Izumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And written right there it says that, at Izumo, after a boisterous and outspoken argument,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the myriad gods decide the relationships between man and woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.47,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(652,421)}Don't they have anything better to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'd ascertained the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be best for me to climb the stairs and see this god face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that god from yesterday went...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha ha, I got you good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or something, I couldn't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd surely end up cursing myself and spending the second half of my life in a right mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that man is really a god,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not like I'm burning with a passionate love;
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would go against my beliefs
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to seek the comfort of a stranger from this transient loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not because I scorn those inexcusable students
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who cannot bear the isolation and greedily seek out others
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I ran to the name of limitless notoriety as "one who hinders love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guise of a barren, agonizing, wretched life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have not I finally reaped the victory close at hand from the endless number of defeats?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would I, the one who hinders love, forgive myself for changing the way I live?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will it end with me providing entertainment to the gods
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the spider's thread to which I cling snaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be happy in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I don't think Akashi-san would be fooled by a freaky, finicky demon like Ozu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like her compassion may be deep enough to find a monstrous man like him intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this continues and Ozu and Akashi-san become friendly with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this will no longer be a problem of my own love;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will become entangled with Akashi-san's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like even my reason was crumbling to pieces like the Castelle before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose to pining for love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The taste is definitely unmatched,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but unfortunately no one knows where they'll set up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ramen stand that comes and goes as it pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go there quite often, yes, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have a good nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm hungry, if I cock my ear I can hear Cat Ramen's wind chime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to try eating there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let go, Akashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I s-s-squished it... I squished it...\N--Now now, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize. I am not fond of moths.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are called Mochiguman, and they come in sets of five, but I have lost one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not! as this earth is round, you are sure to meet once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or if you'd like, I'll help you search for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather you take me to Cat Ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise? Ah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After careful analysis,\Nindeed over-analysis of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I calmly execute a perfect countermeasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, I'm a man who doesn't just hesitate to analyze to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where a perfect countermeasure becomes out of reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Analyzing the number of different patterns of Akashi-san's life and my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I quickly came to a conclusion as to who should become happy, and who should not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the most vexing question of all was whether I,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who had hindered the path of love for countless people,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,could at this juncture change the way I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result of the life or death struggle between love and reason that occurred within me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stumbled in my sleep-deprived state to knock on door 210.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give her to Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Akashi-san to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Good, wait here a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Understood, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me before 8PM on the east side of Kamo-oohashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep moving! Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stopping on top of the bridge is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, So today is Gozan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you will cross this Kamo-oohashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you do, Akashi-san will come walking from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike up a conversation about something and ask her out on a rendezvous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your whining.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something isn't right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to Izuma and being a matchmaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sort of preparation is also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing but a frontal attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining and get out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything until now is water under the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to push forward toward the rose-colored campus life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You escaped safely last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here for Gozan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to come this far despite
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,learning not even the slightest bit about running the path of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just thought something like "that's enough for today," didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't defy the words of a god,\Nhurry up and run along the path of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying this was all your plot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made a wish to the god of matchmaking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to grab this opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't make a serious move now, I'm jumping!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do my love life and you jumping have anything to do with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too sure myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu-san! The river is swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will die if you jump in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got nowhere to run, Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge for the fireworks? But, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu-senpai, have you done some more mischief?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You evil, good-for-nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a friend of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:20:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I don't know Ozu at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't shake off the feeling of regret
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for choosing the tennis circle "Cupid" in front of that fateful clock tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If then I had chosen some other circle, I would have surely spent quite a different two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I could have grasped
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the mystical treasure that is known as that "rose-colored campus life."
